Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.08,0:12:04.79,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}Tinkling Smile 真不可思议 为什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.92,0:12:12.59,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}你一笑起来 心里总会闪亮亮的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.63,0:12:15.13,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}Dest will step 一步一步
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.26,0:12:18.26,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}Dest will skip 一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.19,0:12:30.86,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}回过神来 发现已经着迷了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.94,0:12:36.28,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}"这种事会有的吧?" 你这样说道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.32,0:12:42.08,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}紧紧地握住我的手 体温传达给我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.12,0:12:46.92,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}不管去哪里 都感觉无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.04,0:12:52.96,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}Tin ton tan 跨出那一步的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.01,0:12:58.59,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}世界就像全景画一样 展开了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.05,0:13:03.85,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}Tinkling Smile 无论天空有多宽阔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.89,0:13:09.94,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}如果只有我一人 肯定不会在意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.98,0:13:14.86,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}Tinkling Smile 笑声回响在耳边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.90,0:13:22.87,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}心中充满温柔、愉悦的感觉 还有新的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.12,0:13:28.54,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}一步 一步 前进吧
